    <briefdescription>
<para>JWT data tracking. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>JSON Web Tokens contain several sections, each encoded in Base64URL. This structure tracks the token as it is being built, including limits on the amount of available space. It should be initialized with <ref refid="group__jwt_1gab10ee40ee3c0b3eea98051c2acbb8a75" kindref="member">jwt_init_builder()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
